flash.tools.debugger

Interface IsolateController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PlayerSession

    public interface IsolateController
    Worker specific debug session commands. These are a subset of Session that can be individually routed to a specific worker (including the main worker if the player does not support concurrency). This is implemented by PlayerSession and used by the getWorkerSession() api.
    Author:
    anirudhs
    See Also:
    flash.tools.debugger.IsolateSession, flash.tools.debugger.Session#getWorkerSession(int)
